description: New! First Open House! Beautifully appointed 1 bed + office in the highly sought-after Allele building, located in the vibrant heart of South Boston. Perfectly blending upscale boutique finishes with the comfort of open-concept living, this stylish urban retreat offers everything you need to live, work, and entertain in style.The chef’s kitchen is a true centerpiece, featuring gas cooking, sleek cabinetry, premium stainless steel appliances. The spacious primary bedroom offers a tranquil retreat, while the bonus office space provides the flexibility to work from home in comfort. The luxurious bathroom boasts boutique tilework and a huge walk-in shower with spa-like finishes. Complete with your own private balcony with views to the sea A/C, W/D and deeded garage parking for effortless city living.Located just moments from the Broadway T Station, Whole Foods, top-rated restaurants, and South Boston’s waterfront, this exceptional home offers the perfect blend of location and luxury
